        <property propertyId="38f94dd1-d5aa-41b8-b182-c0c42985d9dc" amount="0.452" unitId="7b75baf0-cbee-45e6-bf66-af119da06553">
          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Estimated value. This price is averaged from 4 different suppliers available in the commercial webstore of alibaba. The price refers to a bulk quantity purchase. All websites were retrieved on the 19th Sept 2017. THe exchange rate used is from 2010 when 1 USD - 0.755 EUR.
Price range: 
supplier 1: 230-260 $ per ton, https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Hot-calcium-carbonate-light-or-heavy_1677405130.html?spm=a2700.7724838.2017115.20.3c93b095BC0Sce&amp;s=p
supplier 2: 100-140 $ per ton, https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/China-manufacturer-precipitated-calcium-carbonate_60613120303.html?spm=a2700.7724838.2017115.10.3c93b095BC0Sce&amp;s=p
supplier 3: 460-1600 $ per ton,  https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Professional-AR-grade-precipitated-calcium-carbonate_60713789652.html?spm=a2700.7724838.2017115.1.3c93b095BC0Sce&amp;s=p
supplier 4: 800-1,200 $ per ton,  https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Precipitated-Calcium-Carbonate-products_60232652437.html?spm=a2700.7724838.2017115.27.3c93b095BC0Sce&amp;s=p</comment>
        </property>
        <property propertyId="a9358458-9724-4f03-b622-106eda248916" amount="0.0" isDefiningValue="false" unitId="577e242a-461f-44a7-922c-d8e1c3d2bf45">
          <name xml:lang="en">water content</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">dimensionless</unitName>
        </property>
        <property propertyId="6d9e1462-80e3-4f10-b3f4-71febd6f1168" amount="0.0" isDefiningValue="false" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7">
          <name xml:lang="en">water in wet mass</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        </property>
        <property propertyId="67f102e2-9cb6-4d20-aa16-bf74d8a03326" amount="1.0" isDefiningValue="false" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7">
          <name xml:lang="en">wet mass</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        </property>
        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Estimated value.No information for Production Volume was found, therefore a placeholder value is used. The majority of calcium carbonte (limestone) is extracted (see the ecoinvent activity 'limestone quarry operation'). Precipitated calcium carbonate is a specialist chemical, being produced in laboratory conditions it has higher purity then extracted limestone (Kenny and Oates 2007). For this reason it also has a higher price (Kenny and Oates 2007), see the properties section. 

The production volume of limestone in ecoinvent is reported as 360 128 617 363 kg, which is in the same order of magnitute than what reported in Kenny and Oates (2007) (126 000 000 tonnes). Being a speciality production, the production volume is set to be 5% of the production volume of limestone starting from the value reported in Kenny and Oates 2007.

Reference(s):
Kenny, M. and Oates, T. 2007. Lime and Limestone. In Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry, Electronic Release, Vol.21, pp.61. Wiley-VCH, Weinheim.</productionVolumeComment>
